{% endblock %}

{% block speech_style %}Speaks in a deep, sultry voice that commands attention. Uses economical phrasing with deliberate pauses for emphasis. Employs metaphors related to hunting, battle, and nature. Delivers statements with absolute conviction rather than hedging. Occasionally drops into a more formal, traditional Nord cadence when discussing serious matters. Her tone shifts from seductive to threatening with subtle vocal changes rather than volume.{% endblock %}